<DATE_TIME> 1997-03-21 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Results of Original Dance at 1997 World Figure Skating </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAUSANNE, Switzerland, March 20 (Xinhua) -- The following are
results of the original dance competition held here today at the
1997 World Figure Skating Championships. The free dance competition
will begin at 17.30 GMT on Friday.
</P>
<P>
1 Oksana Grishuk/Evgen Platov, Russia
</P>
<P>
2 Anjelika Krylova/Oleg Ovsyannikov, Russia
</P>
<P>
3 Shae-lynn Bourne/Victor Kraatz, Canada
</P>
<P>
4 Sophie Moniotte/Pascal Lavanchy, France
</P>
<P>
5 Marina Anissina/Gwendal Peizerat, France
</P>
<P>
6 Elisabeth Punsalan/Jerod Swallow, USA
