<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, March 20 (Xinhua) -- Head of the Liberian interim
government Ruth Perry has said she is not interested in politics
right now but may come into politics in six or seven years if she
is still strong enough.
</P>
<P>
The chairperson of the Liberian Council of State said this
while briefing a group of Nigerian correspondents at the
Executive Mansion in Monrovia on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
