countdown for Hong Kong's return to her motherland was held here
today.
</P>
<P>
In his opening speech, Cheung Wan Fung, chairman and director
of Wen Wei Po, said that thanks to the principle of "One Country,
Two Systems" and the efforts of the broad masses of the Hong Kong
people, Hong Kong is having smooth transition.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong's situation is stable and favorable with sustained
economic growth and great inflows of overseas investment, he said.
</P>
<P>
He said that what is happening here now serves as convincing
proof against all the biased views about Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
