Commerce of Hong Kong, said that with Hong Kong to return to her
motherland in just about one hundred days, there are still lots of
work lying ahead for the Hong Kong people in implementing the
principles of "One Country, Two Systems", "Hong Kong people
governing Hong Kong" and "a High-degree of Autonomy".
</P>
<P>
