Chinese mainland and joint efforts of the Hong Kong people, Hong
Kong will surely achieve its goal of maintaining its prosperity
and stability.
</P>
<P>
About 20 dignitaries from various sectors were present at the
seminar and they delivered speeches or written speeches.  
