<HEADLINE> Western Africa Seeks Police Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, March 21 (Xinhua) -- Police chiefs of Western African
countries are meeting in Nigeria to seek cooperation on cracking
down on criminal activities, especially cross-border crimes.
</P>
<P>
