<HEADLINE> Explosion in Tel Aviv </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, March 21 (Xinhua) -- A bomb went off in a coffee
shop in the center of Tel Aviv this afternoon, killing at least
one and injuring more than 30 others, among them a six-month old
