<TEXT>
<P>
Lagos, March 21 (Xinhua) -- The national leader of the Ntional
Centre Party of Nigeria (NCPN), Chief Don Etiebet, who was detained by
security agents on Sunday has been released, the Daily Times newspaper
reported today.
</P>
<P>
