<HEADLINE> Mahathir Leaves for Saudi Arabia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, March 21 (Xinhua) -- Malaysian Prime Minister
Mahathir Mohamad left here today for Saudi Arabia to receive the
King Faisal International Prize 1997.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir was awarded the King Faisal International Prize
"Service To Islam" and will be presented a certificate, a gold
medallion and 200,000 US dollars at a ceremony at the Al-Khozamah
Center in Riyadh tomorrow, according to an official statement
earlier.
