<HEADLINE> Liverpool Enters Euro Cup Winners Cup Semis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, March 20 (Xinhua) -- Two goals from Robbie Fowler and
one from substitute Stan Collymore gave England's Liverpool a 3-0
victory over Sk Brann of Norway in the second leg of European Cup
Winners' Cup quarter-final in Liverpool on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
